 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">As die snoek loop in die Weskus moet jy snoek gaarmaak.  Ons het gisteraand &#8216;n snoek oor die kole gebraai met suurlemoen en knoffelbotter. Met die snoek wat oor was, het ek viskoekies of visfrikkadelle gemaak.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"/media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-7228\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-600x450.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-300x225.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-750x563.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-500x375.jpg 500w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-380x285.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-760x570.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies2-800x600.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"/media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-7227\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-600x450.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-300x225.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-750x563.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-500x375.jpg 500w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-380x285.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-760x570.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2022/06/Viskoekies3-800x600.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></figure>",
